citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:45 PM on 20-
OCT-2021.
The inspector arrived at 12:45 PM on 20-OCT-2021 to conduct an inspection. There was a gate across the driveway, and
the gate was locked. The inspector immediately attempted to contact the Licensee by telephone (using the contact
information provided), and left a voice message requesting a return phone call. At 12:50 PM, the inspector also
attempted to contact the Licensee via email (using the email address provided).
With no response from licensee, the inspector left the premises at 1:25 PM. The licensee replied via email at 4:48 PM.
End Section
